captions.text: Riot Games Weekly Champion Skin Strategy Meeting
Alright guys, we've been here for a while, we've come up with a lot of good skin ideas. I think that we need to try to like...
Hey Jeff? What's a bro?
What do you mean?
Well I'm on the forums here and there's a thread about ... bro Olaf?
BRO!!
Alright Jeff. Let's hear this idea of yours!
I present to you: Brolaf!
What's a "Bro"?
No. I don't think I'm available for dinner.
Yes, your ELO is very high. Thank you for calling.
Sir? Can I help you?
Not now chief! I'm in the zone.
Sir! You can't go in there!
Your MOM can't go in there!
What kind of bear is that? Is he wearing armor?
Don't worry bros! I'm here to help! I'm from the forums, I heard you were making Brolaf, I want to do my part!
Because look, no offense dudes, but making 10,000 Teemo skins doesn't exactly qualify you for something with this level of badassary!
Look dorks! It's like this. First, you have to have collars. Two of them, and they better be popped!
Why? Because twice the collar equals twice the awesome! It's science.
Two: you got livestrong bracelets. You've got one of them, and then you go out with your boys and drink a lot of Graggy Ice,
and then you wake up somewhere that you're not quite sure of. But it's all good because you've got your second one.
It's your lifeline. It keeps you in there. Twice as strong, live strong, UHHH, YEAH!!!
Do you got this bro?
DO. YOU. GOT. THIS. BRO?
Out of my way loser!
Brooooooo!!!!!
Pound town, dude!
Hey! I've got something for you.
Graggy Ice BRO! Sup dude? Oh yeah. OH YEAH!
BROMACIA!!!!
I came here to kick butt, and drink Graggy. Looks like I'm all out of Graggy.

title: League of Legends - Brolaf, the King of Bromacia
